article_title: UnitedHealth Revamps Management Amid Departure Of Key Executive

article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen

og.description: The nation’s largest health insurer, UnitedHealth Group (UNH), said it has restructured its management team amid the departure of a key executive who oversaw key health plan operations including public exchanges under the Affordable Care Act. UnitedHealth said it is creating a new “Office of the Chief Executive” amid the departure [...]
